# New-card compat (wave 3): Llanowar Elves — scripted ACTIVATED mana ability.
#
# Llanowar Elves is a {G} 1/1 with "{T}: Add {G}."
#   A:AB$ Mana | Cost$ T | Produced$ G
# (CR 605 mana abilities, CR 602 activated abilities.)
#
# Tracking issue: Card Compatibility: Llanowar Elves.
#
# Aspects exercised:
#   1. The body/keywords parse and the creature enters the battlefield (1/1).
#   2. The {T}: Add {G} mana ability produces green mana that is actually
#      USABLE to pay a cost — proven by spending it on a {1}{G} spell.
#
# Scenario:
#   - P0: a Llanowar Elves already in play (no summoning sickness, so it can tap),
#     ONE Forest, and a Grizzly Bears ({1}{G}) in hand.
#   - To cast Grizzly Bears P0 needs {1}{G} = 2 mana. One Forest only makes {G};
#     the SECOND mana MUST come from the Elves (Forest pays {G}, Elves pays the
#     {1} generic). So a successful cast proves the Elves produced usable mana.
#   - Script: P0 casts Grizzly Bears (engine auto-taps Forest + Elves for mana).
#
# HOW TO RUN / VERIFY interactively:
#   mtg tui --start-state test_puzzles/newcard_llanowar_elves_mana.pzl \
#       --p1 heuristic --p2 heuristic --seed 42 -v 2 --no-color-logs

[metadata]
Name:New Card - Llanowar Elves Mana Casts a Creature
Goal:Win
Turns:1
Difficulty:Easy
Description:P0 has a Llanowar Elves and a single Forest; it casts a {1}{G} Grizzly Bears. With only one land, the Elves' {T}: Add {G} ability MUST supply the second mana, so a successful cast proves the mana ability works. Backs Card Compatibility: Llanowar Elves (AB$ Mana, Cost$ T, Produced$ G; CR 605).

[state]
turn=1
activeplayer=p0
activephase=MAIN1
p0life=20
p0hand=Grizzly Bears
p0battlefield=Llanowar Elves;Forest
p0library=Forest;Forest;Forest;Forest;Forest

p1life=20
p1battlefield=
p1library=Mountain;Mountain;Mountain;Mountain;Mountain

[p0_script]
# Cast the {1}{G} Grizzly Bears. The engine pays {G} from the Forest and the
# {1} generic from the Llanowar Elves' tap-for-mana ability.
cast Grizzly Bears

[assertions]
# The {1}{G} creature was successfully cast — only possible if the Elves
# contributed mana (one Forest alone cannot pay {1}{G}).
spell cast Grizzly Bears
# Grizzly Bears resolved onto P0's battlefield (alongside the Elves).
me battlefield contains Grizzly Bears
me battlefield contains Llanowar Elves
